\SE[1]According to plan. \.I think we can proceed without
any problems.

\SE[13]Alright...! \!\SE[14]Then let's go over the operation
plan again!

\SE[11]Why are you taking charge? \SE[12]You're the weakest
one here.

\SE[12]I was appointed as the leader by Vega-san...!
\!\SE[13]And I am not weak!!\. You are underestimating the
importance of defense too much! \!\SE[14]By the way, what is
that ridiculous cosplay supposed to be...!?

\SE[14]W-What...?! You're saying it's ridiculous...!! This
outfit is matching with Vega-sama...! \SE[12]Don't you
understand this cuteness and coolness?!?

\SE[11]Did Vita's mother stay up all night to make this for
me?! \SE[24]You were the lowest piece of garbage who mocked
people's efforts...!!

\SE[14]I didn't say that...!! \SE[13]...Isn't that supposed
to be a proof of recognition? If you wear it, it's like a
cosplay. \SE[52]Besides, I'm not even a student or anything.

\SE[14]What's with these graduates from the school?!
\SE[12]I'm way more excellent than those guys! \SE[40]The
level of the teachers is different! I am a teacher!!

\SE[21]Well...\.That's right.... \!\SE[0]We're going to
review the plan, right?

\SE[14]Save your flirting for later when we get
home!\!\SE[0] Geez.

\SE[33]Ahem.... \SE[12]Let's review the plan again.
\SE[13]This time, we are the guerrilla unit! We will divert
the enemy's attention and support the main force!
\SE[14]So...Melissa-kun! What is the target of this attack?!

\SE[0]Remnants of the Kordain soldiers. \SE[0]Those who have
fallen into banditry have formed a group, causing damage in
the vicinity. Our objective is to suppress or capture them.

\SE[10]Hmm, excellent!! \SE[11]...Now, Ronoa-kun! Please
explain the infiltration route we will be using this time!

\SE[1]We will infiltrate from the river at the side
entrance, following along the mountainside. \!\SE[0] While
weakening the enemy forces and diverting their attention
towards us, we will use Cat-san's escape route for our
retreat.\!\SE[1] That's the plan.

\SE[12]Um, umu! That's a perfect answer! \SE[13]Now,
Rebecca-kun! What will be our actions after the mission is
over?

\SE[14]Huh...! \SE[42]Um... I think... we'll regroup with
the older sisters... \SE[1]and assess the situation, then
divide our personnel to provide support...?

\SE[10]Hmm! You got it right, Rebecca-kun! \SE[10]You
remembered it well! That's impressive!

\SE[48]W-Well, it's not like that...! \SE[20]I-I'm totally
fine with this...!?!
